Class PacketInspectionHandlerWithCheck

  • java.lang.Object
    • node.PacketInspectionHandler
      • node.PacketInspectionHandlerWithCheck
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jnetpcap.packet.PcapPacketHandler<Node_SharedMemory>

    public class PacketInspectionHandlerWithCheck
extends PacketInspectionHandler
    Every time a packet is checked, the exit condition is tested. If the exit condition has been met, it breaks the loop. Otherwise, its functionality is the same as PacketInspectionHandler.
